   139Ôćĺ## API Documentation
   141Ôćĺ### Synchronous API (`Result`) ÔÇŽ
   143Ôćĺ#### `ok`
   145ÔćĺConstructs an `Ok` variant of `Result`
   146Ôćĺ
   147Ôćĺ**Signature:**
   148Ôćĺ
   149Ôćĺ```typescript
   150Ôćĺok<T, E>(value: T): Ok<T, E> { ... }
   151Ôćĺ```
   152Ôćĺ
   153Ôćĺ**Example:**
   154Ôćĺ
   155Ôćĺ```typescript
   156Ôćĺimport { ok } from 'neverthrow'
   157Ôćĺ
   158Ôćĺconst myResult = ok({ myData: 'test' }) // instance of `Ok`
   159Ôćĺ
   160ÔćĺmyResult.isOk() // true
   161ÔćĺmyResult.isErr() // false
   162Ôćĺ```
   163Ôćĺ
