   863Ôćĺ### Asynchronous API (`ResultAsync`)
   865Ôćĺ#### `okAsync`
   867ÔćĺConstructs an `Ok` variant of `ResultAsync`
   868Ôćĺ
   869Ôćĺ**Signature:**
   870Ôćĺ
   871Ôćĺ```typescript
   872ÔćĺokAsync<T, E>(value: T): ResultAsync<T, E>
   873Ôćĺ```
   874Ôćĺ
   875Ôćĺ**Example:**
   876Ôćĺ
   877Ôćĺ```typescript
   878Ôćĺimport { okAsync } from 'neverthrow'
   879Ôćĺ
   880Ôćĺconst myResultAsync = okAsync({ myData: 'test' }) // instance of `ResultAsync`
   881Ôćĺ
   882Ôćĺconst myResult = await myResultAsync // instance of `Ok`
   883Ôćĺ
   884ÔćĺmyResult.isOk() // true
   885ÔćĺmyResult.isErr() // false
   886Ôćĺ```
   887Ôćĺ
